===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Bianca (Masters)}}
Bianca, in her {{B2W2}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Musharna}}, {{p|Virizion}}, and {{p|Chandelure}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Bianca became a playable sync pair on November 14, 2020.

Bianca has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]].

